DOWNLOAD: Scenario Twin Pack - ECML York to Peterborough
A twin pack scenario for the ECML York to Peterborough route and the scenarios are based in 2016. Both scenarios start from Peterborough and finish up at York.
  Train Simulator Downloads   Oct 5, 2021   0   7  Add to Reading List

Download
A twin pack scenario for the ECML York to Peterborough route and the scenarios are based in 2016. Both scenarios start from Peterborough and finish up at York.  This scenario is from Ashley Ballymena one of TSD's new partners.

Requirements:
Armstrong Powerhouse
Class 43 MTU and VP185 Enhancement Packs
Class 91 Enhancement Packs
Class 66 Enhancement Packs
Class 142 Pack
Class 150/2 Pack
Class 150/1 Enhancement Pack
Class 158 Perkins Enhancement Pack
Class 168/170/171 Enhancement Pack
TDA Tanker Wagons
JNA Network Rail Wagons

Alan Thomson Sim
VTEC/LNER HST Class 43 Reskin Pack
VTEC/LNER 225 Class 91 Reskin Pack
HST Mk3 Sliding Doors Pack

Just Trains
Class 60 Advanced Pack
Class 153 Advanced Pack

Major Wales
Revamped HST Pack
Revamped 153 Pack
Be sure to have all the required base packs for the enhancement packs to work properly.

You are welcome to swap trains about in the scenario editor if you wanted to use better trains that you may own already or don't have the required DLC but I am not responsible for any errors if you do this.
Please post any bugs or issues although I have tested this scenario many times and it works fine on my system although it may not work on yours. Use this scenario at your own risk.
Feedback and suggestions are most welcome and please enjoy the scenario.
Please check out my channel "Transport & Simulation Hub" on YouTube for Transport and Gaming videos and please support my creations by liking and sharing :).
